building:
mkdir [topdir]conf/Znc/
cp conf.ini.example [topdir]conf/Znc/conf.ini
add conf/Znc/conf.ini to [topdir]conf/conf.ini  under the [config] section
cp addusertext.txt.example [topdir]addusertext.txt
make clean
make all


copy ZncModule/ircppbot.cpp to the znc source modules directory
make znc and load the module (loadmodule ircppbot)
